1271
00:49:52,708 --> 00:49:55,208
but my folks got it
from the constellation, okay?!

1272
00:49:55,291 --> 00:49:57,375
- How cruel of your parents
to give you

1273
00:49:57,458 --> 00:49:59,291
the name of a group
of brilliant stars

1274
00:49:59,375 --> 00:50:00,375
