1275
00:50:00,458 --> 00:50:04,000
- Forever doomed to be compared
to their great majesty,

1276
00:50:04,083 --> 00:50:06,291
yet you don't shine.
It's rather sad.

1277
00:50:06,375 --> 00:50:09,250
- Why do you two
have to gang up on me like this?

1278
00:50:09,333 --> 00:50:10,708
- Aw, don't worry.
