stars are a symbol of hope,

1280
00:50:12,791 --> 00:50:15,541
which means it's too soon
for you to give up now.

1281
00:50:15,625 --> 00:50:17,375
- Yeah, thanks a lot
for the advice.

1282
00:50:19,500 --> 00:50:21,333
- [gasps]

1283
00:50:21,416 --> 00:50:22,541
Look, look!

1284
00:50:22,625 --> 00:50:25,791
There are so many snow spirits!

1285
00:50:26,833 --> 00:50:28,375
