- [panting]

1390
00:55:56,208 --> 00:55:56,875
Were you waiting long?

1391
00:55:56,958 --> 00:55:59,916
- No. I just got here.

1392
00:56:06,666 --> 00:56:08,541
[gasps]

1393
00:56:08,625 --> 00:56:09,000
Well, all right, then.

